metadata.name: Purple Dream
metadata.description:
You will be disappointed by the people around you, but this is a new beginning  
The ground is cold  
But this warm blood is in your body  
That gives you the courage to continue and you move  
You will see many birds on your way  
who stare at you with their beautiful eyes  
But what do they think about you?  
You hug one of them  
And you want it to stay with you  
But it puts you to sleep with all his beauty and tells you:  
Do not pollute my beauty  
Don't take my wings  
I am not your type  
I will never come down from my height  
pass me by  
And the roof of the world will fall for you  
And you shout loudly:  
So what is beautiful in this world so that I can walk on this cold ground?  
While flying in the sky, it tells you:  
Only you are beautiful  
and live for yourself.
